race.description: Jax Tyres And Auto Caloundra Hcp (BM65)
race.comment: BUNDELLA (6) is first-up here but has tuned up for this with two recent trials and gets the reliable Gollan/Maloney combination. Should be kept very safe while fresh. TAKE A BOW (12) has placed over this track and trip and will be ready to peak now fourth-up from the break. Gets the services of Moor in the saddle and is right in the mix. JOY A PLENTY (8) draws favourably for Huxtable and may give backers a sight over this sprint journey. FIGHTING IDOL (3) gets plenty of weight relief with the 3kg claim and should get a cosy run in transit from the inside marble. Shouldn't be ignored. PLATINUM LIES (7) best of the rest.
